description: This is the number guessing game of “higher or lower.” In this game, Alexa chooses a number between 1 and 100, you try to guess it, and she responds with “higher” or “lower.” Or you can play the other way around, where you choose a number, and Alexa guesses. To get started, ask High Low to guess my number, or ask High Low to think of a number.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask High Low to guess my number.
name: High Low Guessing Game
